  "reference_number": "MAL0012",
  "remarks": "\nMARKO MINING, a Malian company, is an involved person under the Mali (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 on that basis that it is associated with the Wagner Group (now renamed as the “Africa Corps” or “Expeditionary Corps”), being a person which is and has been involved in threatening the peace, stability and security of Mali and/or undermining efforts to implement the Agreement on Peace and Reconciliation in Mali. \n",
